<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_evb_3bs_bx">
 <title>Working with DPM</title>
 <shortdesc>Before you can work with <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/>, you
        must have a <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/>
        organization and user account.</shortdesc>
 <conbody>
  <p>To work with <ph conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"
            />, you complete the following tasks within the <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>
            UI:</p>
        <ul id="ul_bkn_xxf_xw">
            <li>Register <ph
                    conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"
                /> to work with <ph
                    conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"
                />.</li>
            <li>Configure pipelines to aggregate statistics.</li>
            <li>Manage how pipelines work with <ph
                    conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"
                />.</li>
            <li>Optionally, modify <ph
                    conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/>
                configuration properties.</li>
            <li>Optionally, unregister <ph
                    conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"
                /> from working with <ph
                    conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"
                />.</li>
        </ul>
 </conbody>
</concept>
